      "section": [
        "Qin"
      ],
      "text": "War Minister Qin was the overseer of the Fire Nation military's technology, and despite the many failures of his inventions, his technological expertise ensured he remained a valuable member of the Fire Lord's cabinet."
    },
    {
      "body": "An emissary of the Fire Nation for many years, Qin oversaw the creation of all the Fire Nation's war machines and had several secret weapons in the works in an effort to bring victory to the Fire Nation, and an end to the ${link_0}.",
      "links": [
