      ],
      "text": "An emissary of the Fire Nation for many years, Qin oversaw the creation of all the Fire Nation's war machines and had several secret weapons in the works in an effort to bring victory to the Fire Nation, and an end to the Hundred Year War."
    },
    {
      "body": "When the Fire Nation first threatened to burn down the ${link_0}, Qin was able to secure the services of the ${link_1}, who offered to help the Fire Nation in their war effort in exchange for the preservation of the temple. Qin visited the temple regularly to check on his inventions, and their partnership led to the creation of ${link_2} and warships.",
      "links": [
