      "section": [
        "Qin",
        "History"
      ],
      "text": "Months later, Qin revealed his masterpiece, a massive drill developed for the penetration of the Great Walls of Ba Sing Se. However, his plan was foiled again by Team Avatar."
    },
    {
      "body": "After the destruction of the drill, Qin worked to make more war balloons, while adapting and improving the technology to create the larger ${link_0}.",
